  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary hypotheses are that the intervention will improve A1C, blood pressure, lipids,
      weight, self-efficacy, self-management behaviors, and use of clinical services at 12 and 24
      months follow-up.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
